<header>
  <h1>Good Sam Connect</h1>
  <p>People helping people — roadside and real-life emergencies</p>
</header>
<main>
  <section>
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>Good Sam Connect is a <strong>free, community-powered app</strong> that connects people in roadside or real-life emergencies with nearby helpers — from flat tires and medical crises to silent SOS and walking for water. We believe help should be free, fast, and human.</p>
  </section>
  <section>
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Users request help by selecting their emergency type.</li>
      <li>Nearby verified helpers receive alerts and respond quickly.</li>
      <li>Helpers can accept tips or payments through the app.</li>
      <li>AI powers smart routing, safety checks, and escalations.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section>
    <h2>Why Sponsor Good Sam Connect?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Align your brand with a life-saving mission and community impact.</li>
      <li>Gain visibility inside the app, press, and social media.</li>
      <li>Engage your employees as active Good Sams helping the community.</li>
      <li>Transparent impact reporting and PR benefits.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section>
    <h2>Sponsorship Opportunities</h2>
    <p>Become a Founder, Premium Partner, or Supporter with tailored branding packages. Your sponsorship keeps the app free and helpers paid while boosting your brand’s goodwill.</p>
